@startuml
title Threads

autonumber
autoactivate on

box Main Thread
participant GptUiMain
end box

box JavaFX Application Thread
participant GptUiApplication
participant QuestionModel as QuestionModelFx
end box

box Cached Thread Pool (EXECUTOR)
participant QuestionModel as QuestionModelPool
end box

GptUiMain --> GptUiApplication **
GptUiApplication -> QuestionModelFx: requestAnswer()
QuestionModelFx -> QuestionModelPool: runAsync(send)
QuestionModelFx <-- QuestionModelPool
GptUiApplication <-- QuestionModelFx

...answer streams over SSE on the pool thread...
loop each throttled progress tick (~250ms)
QuestionModelPool ->> GptUiApplication: Platform.runLater(progressHtml)
end

QuestionModelPool ->> GptUiApplication: Platform.runLater(callback)

@enduml
